== 製作 ==
2018年5月，據報導，[[史考特·伊斯威特|史考特·伊斯威特]]、[[卡賴伯·蘭里·瓊斯|卡賴伯·蘭里·瓊斯]]和[[奧蘭多·布魯|奧蘭多·布魯]]將主演阿富汗戰爭電影《72小時前哨救援》，由{{le|洛·路瑞|Rod Lurie}}執導，千年傳媒（{{lang|en|Millennium Media}}）製作。該片改編自駐地記者{{le|傑克·泰普|Jake Tapper}}的2012年著作《被遺忘的前哨》（{{lang|en|''The Outpost: An Untold Story of American Valor''}}）。[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2018年8月起開始進行，同時[[米洛·吉勃遜|米洛·吉勃遜]]也加入了演出陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jake-tappers-outpost-film-enlists-scott-eastwood-orlando-bloom-star-1107865|title=Jake Tapper's 'Outpost' Film Enlists Scott Eastwood, Orlando Bloom to Star (Exclusive)|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2018-05-03|accessdate=2018-05-03|archive-date=2018-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503151335/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jake-tappers-outpost-film-enlists-scott-eastwood-orlando-bloom-star-1107865|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.flickeringmyth.com/2018/05/scott-eastwood-and-orlando-bloom-head-to-war-in-the-outpost/|title=Scott Eastwood and Orlando Bloom head to war in The Outpost|work=Flickering Myth|date=2018-05-05|accessdate=2018-05-05}}</ref>。拍攝大多在[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]進行，於2018年10月中旬[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/videos/tv/2018/10/31/lead-outpost-film-nick-paton-walsh-jake-tapper.cnn|title=On location in Bulgaria as 'The Outpost' becomes a feature film|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2018-10-31|accessdate=2020-05-30|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703005603/https://www.cnn.com/videos/tv/2018/10/31/lead-outpost-film-nick-paton-walsh-jake-tapper.cnn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《72小時前哨救援》原定於2020年3月14日在[[西南偏南|西南偏南影展]]首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-01-15/south-by-southwest-film-festival-lineup-judd-apatow-pete-davidson/|title=SXSW Film Festival to premiere Judd Apatow, Pete Davidson comedy|date=2020-01-15|accessdate=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807082854/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-01-15/south-by-southwest-film-festival-lineup-judd-apatow-pete-davidson|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://schedule.sxsw.com/2020/films/2023346|title=SXSW 2020 Schedule - The Outpost|work=SXSW|accessdate=2020-03-05|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305071122/https://schedule.sxsw.com/2020/films/2023346|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但由於[[2019冠状病毒病疫情对电影业的影响|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]的影響而取消<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sxsw.com/2020-event-update/|title=City of Austin Cancels SXSW March Events|website=South by Southwest|date=2020-03-06|accessdate=2020-03-06|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306220834/https://www.sxsw.com/2020-event-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年4月，{{le|銀幕傳媒影業|Screen Media Films}}買下了該片的北美發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-outpost-rod-lurie-scott-eastwood-caleb-landry-jones-orlando-bloom-screen-media-acquisition-1202912293/|title=SXSW Debut Nixed, Rod Lurie-Directed Afghan War Thriller ‘The Outpost’ Lands Screen Media Deal|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2020-04-20|accessdate=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421041747/https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-outpost-rod-lurie-scott-eastwood-caleb-landry-jones-orlando-bloom-screen-media-acquisition-1202912293/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《72小時前哨救援》於2020年7月3日以[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]（VOD）的方式在美國發行<ref>{{cite web |title=Jake Tapper Announces "The Outpost" Film Will Premiere On July 3rd |url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/jake-tapper-announces-outpost-film-073500459.html |website=www.yahoo.com }}{{Dead link}}</ref>，並於7月2日至5日在已恢復營業的影院（500個大銀幕）[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web|title=‘The Outpost' Plots Theatrical Run on 500 Screens in July|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/outpost-plots-theatrical-run-500-screens-july-2-1295671|date=2020-05-22|accessdate=2020-05-30|work=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2020-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531022403/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/outpost-plots-theatrical-run-500-screens-july-2-1295671|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片在臺灣由[[海樂影業|海樂影業]]定於2020年6月24日上映<ref name="@movies" />，成為最早在院線發行該片的市場<ref name="@movies(2020-06-12)">{{cite news|url=http://app2.atmovies.com.tw/news2/NF2006127727/|title=台灣防疫好萊塢佩服《72小時前哨救援》特例讓台灣提早上映|work=開眼電影網|date=2020-06-12|accessdate=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701152604/http://app2.atmovies.com.tw/news2/NF2006127727/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==
《72小時前哨救援》整體獲得了正面居多的評價。[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]]網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於39條評論，該片持有92%的新鮮度，平均評分為7.45／10<ref name="RT">{{cite web|title=The Outpost (2020)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_outpost_2019|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|language=en|access-date=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622070953/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_outpost_2019|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據11篇影評則獲得了69分（滿分100）<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|title=The Outpost Reviews|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-outpost|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|access-date=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704181855/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-outpost|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

